# Build context = repo root. Keep the image lean AND secret-free.
# Anything that could carry secrets, runtime state, or local cruft is excluded
# here as defense-in-depth on top of .gitignore (the build context can include
# gitignored files, so this list is load-bearing for not baking secrets in).

# --- Secrets & runtime config (NEVER bake into a public image) ---
**/.secrets.env
**/config.env
**/*.local

# --- Bot runtime state (locks, leases, worktrees, logs, queue) ---
**/.pr-bot-state/
**/*.log

# --- VCS / tooling ---
.git
.gitignore
.dockerignore
.claude/
.vscode/

# --- Docs & meta (not needed at runtime) ---
**/*.md
LICENSE
ARCHITECTURE.md
docs/

# --- CI definitions ---
azure-pipelines.yml
